node.text:
As of tomorrow 3/25/2020 @precisionweldingacademy will be closed until 4/6/2020. .
Since we are closed, I will be doing a live video demos every day or every other day for our students and anyone else who wants to tune in. .
If there is anything you would like to see or tips leave a comment and I will see if I can get to it! .

node.text:
@lil_araujo03 learning how to weld in our tight weld box! Getting comfortable in uncomfortable positions I crucial, he found out quick walking the cup was a lot more work than just turning up the amps and freehanding everything in.
.
There is a time and a place for everything, learn to be versatile in different techniques and experienced in everything you can!
.
#thatPWASTANDARD #pwa #ckworldwide #outlawleather #thestandardintigwelding #welder #welding #stick #6010 #tig #mig #fluxcore #esab #weldeverydamnday #esabweldingcutting #sparks #esabelite #weldporn
